      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――長瀬麻奈バースデーライブから数日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—A few days after the birthday live for Mana Nagase",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3033.3333333333303,
          "startTime": 3.03333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "ここは……こう！\nいや、ちょっとタイミングが早かった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like this… hah!\nHmmm‚ did I time that a little too fast?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "むぅっ、今のはタイミングは合ってても\nカッコよくはありませんね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmph! Even if I got the timing right‚\nthat wouldn’t have been all that cool.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "力強くかつ、丁寧に華麗に……とうっ！\nはぁ、はぁ、今の感じは――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "More power! More elegance! Haah!\n*huff* *huff* That felt good.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.666666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "うん、いいと思うぞ\n頑張ってるな、こころ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. You’re in the groove now.\nYou’re working hard‚ Kokoro.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.666666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です。今日はおヒマなんですか？\nこんな所で油売って～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello. Don’t you have anything better to do?\nBut just wasting time here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "違う……。みんなの調子を見守るのも\nマネージャーの仕事のうちだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not wasting time. Watching everyone’s\nprogress is also part of a manager's job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.833333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "そんなこと言って、わざわざこころが\n一人の時に来てるじゃないですか～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You say that‚ but it’s strange you turn up\nwhen I’m alone like this!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_02_01-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱりこころに夢中なんですか～？\nダメですよ、こころはみんなのアイドルですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You have a thing for Kokoro‚ don’t you?\nGive it up. I’m everyone’s idol!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}